reviews.review_text:
Sweetness! This show was actually better than NYE in my opinion, although I preferred 12/28 over all 4.  I loved the DPJ with Airto too! Very good Ramble On, and the Stella Blue is the sweetness...
Solid 1991!  This CM SBD is SICK!

More mind left body than dear prudence IMO But under developed, qualifies as neither but could have been either. lol ... Thing I will never forget about this show is meeting a sweet girl from Mass. It was beautiful while it lasted! Nora M if you see this xoxo! Hope you are happy and healthy in life. Much love to you and yours.
Row Jimmy I believe this is one of the best latter-day Row Jimmys. Jerry's flourishes are especially lyrical and focused. (Even) Vince is dialed. Very fine and tight version. Peace.
